org.alljoyn.bus.ifaces
Interface Introspectable

@BusInterface(name="org.freedesktop.DBus.Introspectable")
public interface Introspectable

The standard org.freedesktop.DBus.Introspectable interface. This interface allows bus objects to be introspected for the interfaces that they implement and the child objects that they may contain.

Method Summary
 String Introspect()
          Gets the XML introspection data for the object.
 

Method Detail

Introspect

@BusMethod
String Introspect()
                  throws BusException
Gets the XML introspection data for the object. The schema for the DBus introspection data is described in the DBus specification.

Returns:
XML introspection data for the object
Throws:
BusException
